description: Back in Nashville, Gigi built this bustling business from the ground up with every cupcake she baked. Now, with over 100 locations later, you can also find these insanely tasty treats on the streets of Denver, thanks to Gigi’s Cupcake Bus. You’ll surely adore their gourmet selection of Cheesecakes, Stuffed Cookies, and of course, Cupcakes- with flavors like Peanut Butter Cup, Red Velvet, Strawberries & Cream, and more...your sweet tooth is sure to find these tasty pastries to be a dream come true. These scrumptious goods are an absolute must, so you better hustle on over to Gigi’s Cupcake Bus!
name: Gigi's Cupcake Bus
